// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-4205 — Mass File Rename (sarcoma)
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 2cd6a982-239f-53bd-8713-f18366771049

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
